    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关注</strong>并将我们的系列怪奇小说与宇宙恐怖故事<strong>加入愿望单</strong>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/29f75b0b52c56f363d6891483eb8a4ae.avif?t=1729167631\" width=230 height=86 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/16d8c6ea27ae6a98e8b23a4ebd76df8a.avif?t=1729167631\" width=230 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/fac9db1af8ad4e093fc6eeb07176f7e1.webp?t=1729167631\" width=620 height=16 /></span><strong>!!!  所有收入将捐赠给乌克兰战争中的灾民  !!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >^ 点击查看详情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/fac9db1af8ad4e093fc6eeb07176f7e1.webp?t=1729167631\" width=620 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>我是约翰·琼斯，是我写下了字条上的字 我的船很快就要沉没了，但是船上装着一批宝藏 此刻我就在航海图上标记的*位置</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/a0eca7da09be9acfe672d698ce43096c.avif?t=1729167631\" width=500 height=349 /></span> 加入威廉·琼斯船长，与他的队伍一同踏上<strong>寻宝冒险之旅</strong>！<i>小小玻璃瓶</i>是《Dagon》的第二份官方DLC，改编自怪诞小说大师人生中第一部流传下来的作品，而且写就之时他……<strong>年仅7岁</strong>！稍稍远离星辰噩梦与水下的恐怖存在，体验H·P·洛夫克拉夫特年轻时候更为幽默的一面！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索<strong>7岁洛夫克拉夫特的心灵世界</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在休憩时间踏上一段短暂的冒险之旅（全长不超过<strong>10分钟</strong>） </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解有关<strong>洛夫克拉夫特童年</strong>的有趣细节 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>拥有完整配音的3D游戏世界中</strong>体验洛夫克拉夫特创作的短篇故事 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原作的电子书与有声读物版本（包含多种格式与语言），官方壁纸 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含<strong>洛夫克拉夫特童年时期完整留下的全部4篇创作</strong>的电子书（仅提供英文版）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/c211b2a700fc14c07bcb0b2adf7a3539.avif?t=1729167631\" width=216 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >访问文件方法：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的Steam库中右击<strong>Dagon</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择<strong><i>管理&gt;</i></strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击<strong><i>浏览本地文件</i></strong></p></li></ul>",
